============================================================
✨ Key Takeaways:
  • explore() generates multiple variants of a function
  • Use test= to filter by correctness
  • Use benchmark= to select by performance
  • The winning variant is cached to .wishful/
  • verbose=True shows beautiful progress (default)
  • save_results=True exports to CSV (default)
